			<header class="entry-header">
				<h3 class="entry-title"><a href="http://hennessysview.com/2012/04/15/down-at-the-lake-they-want-to-know-is-the-tea-party-dead/" title="Permalink to Down at the Lake, They Want to Know &#8220;Is the Tea Party Dead?&#8221;" rel="bookmark">Down at the Lake, They Want to Know &#8220;Is the Tea Party Dead?&#8221;</a></h3>
			</header><!-- .entry-header -->

		</article>

