									</div><!-- .comment-meta .commentmetadata -->
			</footer>

			<div class="comment-content"><p>You&#8217;re right Kevin I see that too. I see alot of so called grassroots organizers organizing petty infighting attacks on each other instead of acting how they preach at events and book signings. </p>
</div>

